(Denmark), Henry (France), Zidane (France), Ortega (Argentina), Ronald
De Boer (Netherlands), Overmars (Netherlands), Ince (England), Cocu
(Netherlands), Asanovic (Croatia), Hierro (Spain)
</P>
<P>
Strikers: Hernandez (Mexico), Ilie (Romania), Batistuta
(Argentina), Vieri (Italy), Bierhoff (Germany), Salas (Chile), Owen
(England), Flo (Norway), Ronaldo (Brazil), Brian Laudrup (Denmark),
Suker (Croatia), Bergkamp (Netherlands)
