<HEADLINE> UNEP Chief Applauses Sino-US Environmental Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, July 8 (Xinhua) -- Many of the environmental
programs agreed to by China and the U.S. recently in Beijing
reflect U.N. Environment Program's new areas of focus, UNEP
