friendship to an even higher level.
</P>
<P>
Further consolidating the advance of Sino-Japanese relations
accords with the common interest and aspirations of the two
peoples, and also constitutes an important component of the peace,
stability and development of Asia, Li said, adding that both sides
should cherish and contribute more to their hard-won friendship.
</P>
<P>
Kazutoshi agreed that Kobe and Tianjin have actively
communicated since forging their sister-city relationship. Tianjin
has undergone enormous changes, while Kobe is experiencing a
resurrection as it recovers from a massive earthquake, he said,
expressing the hope that cooperation between the two cities will
further expand. 
</P>
