southwest China's Yunnan Province, with Ha Giang in Vietnam.
</P>
<P>
The new 143-km bus route, the first passenger service initiated
between the two countries some three months ago, has attracted a
constantly increasing number of passengers crossing the border for
either business or sightseeing.
</P>
