envoy, urged in Luanda that both the government and UNITA should
make greater effort in implementing the Lusaka Peace Protocol.
</P>
<P>
UNITA should bear the major responsibility for the current
crisis for delaying the implementation of the peace deal by
refusing to hand over the four sensitive areas in central Angola.
