<HEADLINE> Nagano Olympics Gain Surplus, Official Says </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, July 9 (Xinhua) -- Strong sales and a weaker yen helped
the Nagano Winter Olympics post a 4.5 billion yen (32 million
U.S. dollars) surplus, an organizing committee official said
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
